Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.18,0:01:52.34,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,350)}現在的內心裏
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.43,0:01:57.17,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,350)}就像雪一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.37,0:01:59.70,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,350)}堆積起了
