Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,------main------
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.13,0:00:13.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桂同學  今天也沒來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.35,0:00:16.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,委員會很忙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.20,0:00:18.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.62,0:00:19.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.01,0:00:23.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誠  這樣真的好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.71,0:00:24.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.69,0:00:30.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看  最近  早上你也故意錯開時間…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.61,0:00:34.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我呢  和世界在一起就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.03,0:00:38.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  雖然很高興…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.23,0:00:39.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就沒事了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.16,0:00:40.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.41,0:00:42.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.58,0:00:55.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  不過稍微有點變冷了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.53,0:00:56.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.12,0:01:00.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起在房頂上吃飯的日子也結束了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.03,0:02:44.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼  誠君會和西園寺同學做那樣的事…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.78,0:02:50.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誠君…開始討厭我了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.22,0:02:58.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不多加努力是不行的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.33,0:03:05.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.68,0:03:12.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐  聽說馬上就要開學園祭了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.40,0:03:16.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.28,0:03:18.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也去看看  可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.83,0:03:19.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.91,0:03:20.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.86,0:03:22.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誠哥哥也在的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.20,0:03:24.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.98,0:03:32.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的借到了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.33,0:03:36.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家  聽我說
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.77,0:03:38.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼  怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.62,0:03:43.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才聽到的  一班是妹妹咖啡屋  二班是殭屍咖啡屋
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.39,0:03:46.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妹妹和殭屍…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.67,0:03:49.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大哥哥～
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.13,0:03:53.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎光臨
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.19,0:03:56.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.05,0:03:59.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像二班抄襲了我們和四班的計劃
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.04,0:04:02.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說是鬼屋和咖啡屋的結合產物
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.15,0:04:06.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管是抄襲還是什麼  是用咖啡屋這事向我們挑釁吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.71,0:04:07.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就接受他們的挑戰
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.82,0:04:09.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剎那
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.04,0:04:13.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界  告訴大家接待客人的訣竅
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.90,0:04:18.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是照著打工處的手冊上教的現學現賣能行的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.28,0:04:21.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且  正式開始之前要好好練習
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.31,0:04:24.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,招攬顧客的宣傳員要穿著可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.20,0:04:27.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提供高級服務的話  是不會輸給那些雜耍的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.00,0:04:29.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剎  剎那
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.22,0:04:32.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打倒一班和二班
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.90,0:04:34.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.80,0:04:36.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.46,0:04:39.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊  妹妹和殭屍的話  我剛才已經…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.44,0:04:42.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼  不是那樣  田中他…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.79,0:04:43.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,田中
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.28,0:04:48.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨晚自己練習時候骨折了  要兩周才能痊癒
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.53,0:04:51.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.57,0:04:53.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是說那個像重裝坦克一樣的男人嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.22,0:04:57.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是柔道部之星  他也是凡人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.09,0:05:00.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是  那樣實行員就…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.58,0:05:02.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就剎那一個人了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.35,0:05:08.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  言葉是一個人做的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.41,0:05:11.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊藤  你不是有空嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.16,0:05:14.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你來頂替田中的位置吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.89,0:05:15.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.81,0:05:17.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又沒有參加社團活動
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.10,0:05:19.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泰介也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.10,0:05:23.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,澤  澤永…我們組要用他
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.91,0:05:24.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.87,0:05:28.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那  那麼  我也幫你們做些什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.91,0:05:30.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擔心桂同學嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.38,0:05:33.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼  吵架了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.18,0:05:34.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.14,0:05:36.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們分手了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.82,0:05:37.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.63,0:05:39.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,清浦  你說什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.58,0:05:41.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在是和世界在交往吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.93,0:05:42.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.43,0:05:43.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.52,0:05:44.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剎  剎那
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.01,0:05:45.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.55,0:05:47.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剎那
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.27,0:05:55.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我說  還需要三塊膠合板
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.77,0:05:59.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行的  各班的比例是定好的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.88,0:06:01.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定有剩下的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.89,0:06:03.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能會有…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.98,0:06:06.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難得我們特意來幫你的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.72,0:06:10.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,材料不齊的話  可就進行不下去了…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.84,0:06:17.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們班只有你一個實行委員  都得靠你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.40,0:06:24.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.69,0:06:27.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼如何  南
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.33,0:06:29.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OK
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.41,0:06:49.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做好準備了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.73,0:06:53.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是這個意思
