Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.82,0:19:26.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我聽剎那說了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.69,0:19:27.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.42,0:19:34.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剎那明明阻止過的  但誠還是去追桂同學了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.76,0:19:40.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剎那還對我道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.60,0:19:44.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是清浦對言葉有偏見
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.62,0:19:50.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界不也一直覺得對不起言葉嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.64,0:19:51.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然是那樣  但…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.86,0:20:00.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.59,0:20:02.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我查了下家庭地址…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.26,0:20:04.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有話想對你說…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.28,0:20:11.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在學校總說不上兩句
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.53,0:20:13.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手機也有問題
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.37,0:20:17.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  對…對不起  是我的手機有問題
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.01,0:20:18.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.31,0:20:20.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在已經沒問題了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.24,0:20:26.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拒絕來電？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.33,0:20:28.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不用做到這地步…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.83,0:20:29.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必須得這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.23,0:20:32.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剎那
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.04,0:20:37.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.75,0:20:41.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以還可以發短信什麼的了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.82,0:20:43.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.15,0:20:45.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以  那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.05,0:20:46.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.93,0:20:50.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實我  身…身體有點不舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.01,0:20:53.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.30,0:20:54.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.75,0:20:56.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然想請你進來坐坐  但…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.44,0:21:00.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.79,0:21:09.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那  沒辦法呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.81,0:21:15.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  可以問一句嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.17,0:21:17.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.37,0:21:19.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是關於後夜祭的事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.24,0:21:23.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能和我一起跳舞嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.40,0:21:27.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,後夜祭？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.84,0:21:28.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.94,0:21:32.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我被澤永同學邀請了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.75,0:21:36.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.81,0:21:41.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,澤永同學以為我和誠君分手了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.95,0:21:43.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很可笑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.25,0:21:49.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明明一直都是誠君的女朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.57,0:21:55.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.13,0:21:58.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了  我會考慮的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.20,0:22:01.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.83,0:22:02.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,約好了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.39,0:22:11.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.42,0:22:14.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.80,0:22:21.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在出去的話會和言葉…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.77,0:22:22.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.38,0:22:26.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.02,0:22:57.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你太卑鄙了  西園寺同學
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.11,0:23:29.98,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,Scroll up;0;396;13;0,{\frz-90}繰り返す言葉は今も
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.17,0:23:38.42,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,Scroll up;0;396;13;0,{\frz-90}あなたへ届くようにと願ってる
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.75,0:23:45.72,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,Scroll up;0;396;13;0,{\frz-90}いつからか揺らいだ世界
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.89,0:23:52.82,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,Scroll up;0;396;13;0,{\frz-90}すれ違う想い交差する
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.62,0:23:57.38,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,Scroll up;0;396;11;0,{\frz-90}星空に願いを
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.65,0:24:01.37,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,Scroll up;0;396;11;0,{\frz-90}大地に祈りを
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.70,0:24:08.40,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,Scroll up;0;396;13;0,{\frz-90}消えない愛だと誓うの
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.24,0:24:13.40,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,Scroll up;0;396;9;0,{\frz-90}私だけを私だけを
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.62,0:24:17.31,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,Scroll up;0;396;9;0,{\frz-90}抱き締めて欲しいの
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.54,0:24:21.28,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,Scroll up;0;396;9;0,{\frz-90}我が侭なその手強く
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.52,0:24:24.67,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,Scroll up;0;396;9;0,{\frz-90}苦しい程に
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.99,0:24:29.14,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,Scroll up;0;396;8;0,{\frz-90}あなただけをあなただけを
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.41,0:24:33.15,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,Scroll up;0;396;9;0,{\frz-90}求めては生きてる
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.32,0:24:42.88,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,Scroll up;0;396;13;0,{\frz-90}記憶の海の底にひとり溺れてたまま
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.11,0:23:29.98,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,Scroll up;0;396;13;0,{\frz-90}重複的每一句話
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.17,0:23:38.42,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,Scroll up;0;396;14;0,{\frz-90}如今都希望傳到你的耳邊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.75,0:23:45.72,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,Scroll up;0;396;13;0,{\frz-90}從何時起　那搖擺不定的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.89,0:23:52.82,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,Scroll up;0;396;13;0,{\frz-90}擦身而過的思念彼此交織
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.62,0:23:57.38,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,Scroll up;0;396;11;0,{\frz-90}向星空許願
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.65,0:24:01.37,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,Scroll up;0;396;11;0,{\frz-90}向大地祈禱
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.70,0:24:08.40,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,Scroll up;0;396;13;0,{\frz-90}誓下永不消逝的愛情
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.24,0:24:13.40,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,Scroll up;0;396;9;0,{\frz-90}希望　希望我
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.62,0:24:17.31,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,Scroll up;0;396;9;0,{\frz-90}只被你擁入懷中
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.54,0:24:21.28,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,Scroll up;0;396;9;0,{\frz-90}任性的那份執著
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.52,0:24:24.67,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,Scroll up;0;396;9;0,{\frz-90}引向痛苦的深處
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.99,0:24:29.14,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,Scroll up;0;396;9;0,{\frz-90}希望　希望你
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.41,0:24:33.15,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,Scroll up;0;396;9;0,{\frz-90}只想要活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.32,0:24:42.88,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,Scroll up;0;396;13;0,{\frz-90}也許現在你獨自沉溺在記憶之海底吧
